{"tid":566921,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[全新螢幕技術登場] 僅1mm 薄，能舒適地貼在皮膚上輸出畫面！","createTime":"2018-02-20T11:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:54:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28d3e034ddf946ce759e4b3418e17e10d5f17723","tid":566921,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"螢幕技術的突破，除了在電視或者手機上可以看到的色彩和畫素提升，醫療方面的應用也不在少數。東京大學的研究人員最近就開發出新的彈性螢幕，可以貼在皮膚上顯示脈搏速度等各樣資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/20095927/Electronic-skin-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F20095927%2FElectronic-skin-2.jpg&h=b1a48454&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/02/20/japan-skin-electronics-display-micro-led/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2Fjapan-skin-electronics-display-micro-led%2F&d=%2Fd4RTiGqAtN9HQfMtucQB8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=cef0ab6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/02/20/japan-skin-electronics-display-micro-led/</a>"},{"pid":"50814b93f700f967371f51977bf58021cfd516fe","tid":566921,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"這個螢幕採用透氣的微型網狀電極配合可伸展的線路和 Micro LED 燈，做到相當纖薄彈性的效果，雖然畫素有限，不過只有 1mm 薄的設計，方便舒適地貼在皮膚上同時顯示重要資訊。這個螢幕同時可以探測脈搏速度，並連接智慧手機把相關資訊傳送到雲端系統，對於擔心心臟健康的人來說，比穿戴式裝置更為方便。其發光設計，更可以在較暗的地方也顯示資訊。其實類似的技術之前已經有出現，但這次的新設計則有更長的使用壽命，並有更佳的貼合能力。"},{"pid":"9c55ece2618a25543bbf144afecd4c87dfaede6b","tid":566921,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"負責製作的大日本印刷表示，希望在未來 3 年內實現這個技術，讓這個技術更加可靠並開始量產。如果實際商品化的話，可以用來協助在家護養的病人，為他們顯示重要身體狀況之餘，可以同步通知家人或醫療機構跟進。這樣的技術在醫療以外，也可望有其他針對一般消費者的應用之處，未來的穿戴式裝置，可能會有截然不同的形態。"},{"pid":"f180f73310e6249cb50c9ad7f966b327f364e6ec","tid":566921,"uid":35070,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.mentalfloss.com/sites/default/files/styles/mf_image_3x2/public/teletubbieshed.jpg?itok=4Qbgfp51&amp;resize=1100x740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.mentalfloss.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmf_image_3x2%2Fpublic%2Fteletubbieshed.jpg%3Fitok%3D4Qbgfp51%26resize%3D1100x740&h=61e3b7ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f36f5254c3b8f82e776cd6ec22502d5c66c4f1f","tid":566921,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"好快會出現電視M巾"},{"pid":"b09e0eb84d8c8f07e5b1d619ecd0ee9fce46cdf4","tid":566921,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9162cdc4e462b74c07be8bf8faf105aa4dfefc5","tid":566921,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}